---
title: Honey Chermoula Beef and Charred Courgette with Dill Yoghurt and Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Honey Chermoula Beef and Charred Courgette in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
